        repo.save(user);
    } catch (DataAccessException e) {
        // handle all DB errors here
    }
    Internal Working: DB Exception → Exception Translator → DataAccessException
   
    Common Exceptions:
    Exception	                            Meaning
    DuplicateKeyException	                Unique constraint
    DataIntegrityViolationException	      Constraint issue
    EmptyResultDataAccessException	      No data

    Why Important? ✔ DB-independent error handling ✔ Clean architecture

    What enables exception translation? ✔ @Repository
